===Noun===
'''peppermint'''
{{wikipedia}}

#A [[hybrid]] [[herb]] of the mint family formed by crossing [[watermint]] and [[spearmint]].  It has a high [[menthol]] content and a sharp flavor.  Used in cooking, especially in [[herb tea]]s and [[confection]]s.
#A [[confection]] containing extract of peppermint.


